==Trivia==
*"Noamsky" was the main character in ''[[The Glamorous Life of Sachiko Hanai]]'', [[Shit_nobody_cares_about|a highly intelligent and politically subversive porno]].

==Trolling Chomskyites==
A surefire way to piss any Chomskyite off is to say something along the lines of "Chomsky isn't a true anarchist because [[derp]] da durpy durr."

The [http://rubberducky.org/cgi-bin/chomsky.pl/ Chomskybot], a program constructed by [[LOL|John Lawler]] of the University of Michigan and John Sowa, mathematically generates Chomsky-esque text using phrases from his collected works. While all [[over 9000|22 septillion]] possible paragraphs may be grammatically correct, they don't make any rhetorical sense.

